modName: High Definition Vampire Eyes Updated for Dawnguard
summary: A gold and green retexture of the eyes for vampires, now updated for Dawnguard
descriptionHtml:
This is a golden, wolflike recolor of the vampire eyes, including pupils.

To install, extract the ZIP file to your skyrim folder, or use the mod manager: use \'showracemenu\' in the console to set the new texture for your eyes.
author: Sysiphuslove

files.name: High Definition Vampire Eyes Updated for Dawnguard
